com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger

Interface PosTag

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<PosTag>, Serializable, TokenTag

    public interface PosTag
extends TokenTag, Serializable, Comparable<PosTag>
    A part of speech tag, representing a certain morpho-syntaxic category for a word.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static PosTag NULL_POS_TAG
      A null pos tag, to be used for empty tokens that should be discarded.

      The code to be used by the null pos tag.
      static PosTag ROOT_POS_TAG
      An artificial pos-tag used to indicate the artificial root added to all sentences for parsing.

      The code to be used by the root pos tag.
